0th.270: April 13, 2020 - Ellettsville, Indiana USA: A volunteer holds fruit while helping distribute food at Pantry 279 to help those experiencing food insecurity during the COVID-19/Coronavirus stay-at-home order in Indiana during the pandemic. Hoosiers have been ordered to only travel for essential needs. (Jeremy Hogan/Polaris)
